# CSS local style

**Spec:** [040-css-primitives-usage.md](../../specs/040-css-primitives-usage.md)

- **Use CSS classes for all local `<style>` selectors.** Target state/variants with classes (e.g. `class:variant-name={condition}`) and `.base-class.variant-name`, not `&[data-*]`.
- **Exception:** When overriding CSS variables, use nested `&[data-*]` on the class.
